gan construction in 2007, uses portions of what was once planned to be the Outer Beltway in Montgomery and Prince George's counties in Maryland\n** [[Fairfax County Parkway]] and [[Prince William Parkway]], portions of which are built on rights-of-way acquired for the Outer Beltway in Virginia\n\n==Notes==\n{{reflist|group=lower-alpha}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Attached KML|display=title,inline}}\n{{commons category|Interstate 495 (Capital Beltway)}}\n* [http://www.mdroads.com/routes/is495.html I-495 @ MDRoads.com]\n* [http://www.capitalbeltway.mdprojects.com/ Official Study Website published by the Maryland State Highway Administration]\n* [http://www.roadstothefuture.com/Capital_Beltway.html Capital Beltway (I-495 and I-95)], by Roads to the Future\n* [http://www.dcroads.net/roads/capital-beltway/ Steve Anderson's DCroads.net: Capital Beltway (I-495 and I-95)]\n* [https://www.washingtonpost.com/ac2/wp-dyn/A64110-2004Aug13?language=printer \"Memory Lanes\": 40th anniversary of the Beltway's opening (''Washington Post'')]\n* [http://www.lewisandtompkins.com/library/dangers-of-driving-on-the-capital-beltway-dc.cfm Dangers of Driving on the Capital Beltway & Washington D.C.]\n* [http://ghostsofdc.org/2012/03/08/washingtons-circumferential-highway-fighting-over-the-capital-beltway/ Washington's Circumferential Highway: Fighting Over the Capital Beltway]\n\n{{3di|95}}\n{{Streets in Washington, DC}}\n\n[[Category:Interstate Highways in Washington, D.C.|95-4]]\n[[Category:Interstate Highways in Maryland|95-4]]\n[[Category:Interstate Highways in Virginia|95-4]]\n[[Category:Auxiliary Interstate Highways|95-4 Capital Beltway]]\n[[Category:Beltways in the United States|495 Capital Beltway]]\n[[Category:Interstate 95|4 Capital]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Alexandria, Virginia|Interstate 495]]\n[[Category:Transportation in Fairfax County, Virginia|Interstate 495]]\n[[Category:Roads in Prince George's County, Maryland|Interstate 95-4]]\n[[Cate